### Admins API Tests

# Lấy tất cả admin
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admins

###

# Lấy admin với phân trang và tìm kiếm
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admins?page=1&limit=10&search=admin

###

# Lấy chi tiết admin theo ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admins/674b2f8e123456789abcdef8

###

# Tạo admin mới
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admins
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin_spa",
  "email": "admin@spa.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "fullName": "Nguyễn Văn Admin",
  "phone": "0987654321",
  "role": "admin",
  "permissions": ["read", "write", "delete"],
  "isActive": true
}

###

# Tạo super admin
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admins
Content-Type: application/json

